CREATE TABLE [dbo].[FAMILY_LIST] (
    [OWNER_ID]              VARCHAR (50) NOT NULL,
    [PARENT_ID_01]          VARCHAR (50) NULL,
    [PARENT_NAME_01]        VARCHAR (50) NULL,
    [PARENT_BIRTHDATE_01]   DATE         NULL,
    [PARENT_NATIONALITY_01] VARCHAR (50) NULL,
    [PARENT_ID_02]          VARCHAR (50) NULL,
    [PARENT_NAME_02]        VARCHAR (50) NULL,
    [PARENT_BIRTHDATE_02]   VARCHAR (50) NULL,
    [PARENT_NATIONALITY_02] DATE         NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_FAMILY_LIST] PRIMARY KEY NONCLUSTERED ([OWNER_ID] ASC) NOT ENFORCED
)
WITH (HEAP, DISTRIBUTION = ROUND_ROBIN);
